page.title: 11BRACKNELL SWIMMING CLUB
page.content:
{
Every Tuesday evening and Thursday morning,I go swimming at{Bracknell Leisure Centre,where I train with Bracknell Swimming Club,for galas. Although we train very hard I get a lot of enjoyment out of it. Below are my recent times for all four strokes: {50 metres Butterfly:1min 1second { " " Backcrawl:55 seconds { " " Breaststroke:49 seconds { " " Freestyle:39 seconds { Every Tuesday evening I train for 2 hours non stop(7pm - 9pm). Every Thursday morning I train for 1 hour and a quarter(6.15am _ 7.30am) I get back at 7.45am,ready for school.
